Class Percussion

  • java.lang.Object
    • Instrument
      • Percussion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bongos, CrashCymbals, Maracas, Timpani, Xylophone

    abstract class Percussion
extends Instrument
    Percussion.java represents a percussion instrument that inherits from Instrument, and is a superclass of Timpani, Maracas, Bongos, Xylophone, and CrashCymbals.
